# Node / build artifacts
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Repo cruft
.git
.github
docs
.claude
.DS_Store
# NOTE: `agent/` is intentionally NOT ignored — the rigel-assistant image builds
# from the repo root (context: .) so it can pull in both `agent/` and the shared
# `packages/k8s/` source for the esbuild bundle. The `**/node_modules` + `**/dist`
# globs above already keep that context lean. (Other images don't COPY agent/.)
